The above knitted fabrics for seamless underwear were first subjected to a pre-treatment with the following condition in washing. The process is schematically shown in Figure 9:


W100 (detergent): 5 ml (water 10 L);

temperature: 80–90℃;

time: 30 min;

overflow rinse at 80℃;

one rinse cycle at 60℃.

Figure 9.
Pre-treatment process of the fabrics.
